name: 🍾🍾🍾 Frida Punk 099 - FRIxDIEGO 🍾🍾🍾
description:
Frida Kahlo X Diego Rivera

An Artist in love with another Artist.
So much in love they married twice. There was much Frida had to say about her love of Diego.

“I have suffered two grave accidents in my life, one in which a streetcar knocked me down—the other accident is Diego.” - Frida Kahlo
